{"tid":905430,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國知名街霸電競選手 Infiltration 涉虐妻　被罰停賽 13 個月","createTime":"2018-11-17T06:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T08:37:43.000Z","uid":51464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f11829439eb24383bccaf650c35f97c2a6577d1","tid":905430,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:22:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2210419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2210419&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=72e11224\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2210419</a><br />\n電競選手是公眾人物，一旦做出影響公眾形象的事情，隨時會令個人電競事業毀掉。韓國知名《Street Fighter V（街頭霸王 V、快打旋風 V）》電競選手 Infiltration（Lee Seon-woo），最近便因為去年涉毆打當時妻子的家庭暴力事件，被 Capcom 判罰他退出 Capcom Pro Tour 2018 賽季和 Capcom Pro Tour 2019 賽季的賽事，同時他亦被旗下 Panda Global 電競戰隊解約。<br />\n======<br />\n韓國仔打老婆世界第一！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eca3b96dd0fffc1cfee5fa00395a5a3093349f","tid":905430,"uid":47112,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"打街霸勁<br />\n估唔到真人都有返兩吓散手"},{"pid":"c8c04494687318391c07407037b05b6265a94cb2","tid":905430,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f782cba77c4e2c40eb3af094c30abefee465d56","tid":905430,"uid":40925,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime